MAIN_MESSAGE: There is power cut in the KY10 and KY16 areas of Anstruther and St Andrews. We had no advance warning of this and only became aware of it at 9:24am. Our control centre will attempt to reset the network remotely to restore power in stages, and our engineers have arrived onsite in the local area to investigate the fault. Our team will work to get your power back on as quickly and as safely as possible by 11:30am. We apologise for the inconvenience and thank you for your patience. This message was updated at 10:42am on Sunday, 01 November 2020
